INSTALLATION

Installation of the DSD package simply requires the user to clone repository
and type:

cmake .
make
export STACCATO_DIR="your/path/to/dir/STACCATO-1.2"

For correct work with project Utopia EDA please keep STACCATO_DIR
variable and its value in your system permanently.
